Package: armor-pilot
Version: 0.3.8
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17)
Maintainer: VNNIC Lab <tructet@vnnic.vn>
Homepage: https://github.com/Kaint2051/armor-pilot
Description: ArmorPilot - Kubernetes Runtime Security Console
 Web-based management console for vArmor/ArmorPilot Kubernetes security
 policies. Provides a browser UI to create, review, approve and monitor
 security profiles on your Kubernetes cluster.
 .
 Features:
  - Policy lifecycle management (create, review, approve, reject)
  - Enterprise license support
  - Multi-user with role-based access control
  - Hardware-bound license verification
